00:21:28,390 --> 00:21:30,700
Shall we?

298
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:32,810
Thank you.

299
00:21:34,250 --> 00:21:37,670
Everyone who wants a picture, please come to the front.

300
00:21:37,670 --> 00:21:39,650
Yes.

301
00:21:39,650 --> 00:21:42,740
There, look at your mom.

302
00:21:45,210 --> 00:21:47,940
Six years ago he was a whistleblowing hero

303
00:21:47,940 --> 00:21:52,410
- and now he's a Landmine Hero?
- Thank you.

304
00:21:52,410 --> 00:21:57,220
That human is not one with character enough to go into a minefield for his subordinate,

305
00:21:57,220 --> 00:22:02,680
because he made fake evidence to corner and push my father off a cliff.

306
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:06,490
