00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:41,640
Is this something you planned, too?

309
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:44,950
Answer me.

310
00:22:44,950 --> 00:22:46,880
No.

311
00:22:57,940 --> 00:23:03,240
I'll give you the report on the shooting of Won Gi Chun, Division Commander.

312
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:05,590
The culprit who fired is one of my soldiers?

313
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:11,340
According to the results of the military police's investigation, 4th Division's Lee Han Yong. No...

