409
00:29:59,370 --> 00:30:01,900
I'm being forced to do this since it's my job.

410
00:30:01,900 --> 00:30:03,920
It was a blank bullet.

411
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:07,050
I guess you haven't even read the reports.

412
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:13,950
Do you know the name of the soldier you're defending?

413
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:16,760
That little bast—

414
00:30:17,610 --> 00:30:19,100
What good would knowing his name do?

415
00:30:19,100 --> 00:30:22,770
If you act this way, who is the soldier supposed to trust?

416
00:30:22,770 --> 00:30:26,450
He already can't trust military personnel as it is.

417
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:31,360
I mean, whose side are you on right now?

418
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:34,990
Why don't you be a lawyer in my place then, instead of a prosecutor?

419
00:30:34,990 --> 00:30:38,510
Aren't I right, Bae Man?

420
00:30:38,510 --> 00:30:43,440
If you don't do your job properly in court, I'll raise an issue.

421
00:30:48,940 --> 00:30:53,610
What a total jerk. How dare she tell me what to do?

