00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:59,220
Yes. She hasn't been here long. Please forgive her attitude.

424
00:30:59,220 --> 00:31:03,750
What about you? You're going to just watch as your successor talks down to your superior?

425
00:31:03,750 --> 00:31:07,650
Sometimes successors teach things to their predecessor.

426
00:31:07,650 --> 00:31:10,810
What? Are you directing that towards me?

427
00:31:10,810 --> 00:31:13,660
I'm talking about myself.

428
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:16,000
I'll see you in court.

429
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:18,330
Unity.

430
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:35,270
Why do you think Corporal Kim Han Yong shot you?

431
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:39,720
Probably because he's family.

432
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:46,130
He probably wanted to let his anger out somehow, watching his half-dead brother.

433
00:31:47,450 --> 00:31:52,130
