00:32:14,130 --> 00:32:20,650
However, I do not regret entering the land mine.

441
00:32:22,780 --> 00:32:25,370
Let's take a break.

442
00:32:29,490 --> 00:32:31,940
Thank you so much for making time today.

443
00:32:31,940 --> 00:32:34,660
Thank you for your work.

444
00:32:34,660 --> 00:32:36,330
- Thank you.
- Get well soon!

445
00:32:36,330 --> 00:32:37,510
Yes, please recover soon!

446
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:40,580
Thank you. Get home safely.

447
00:32:40,580 --> 00:32:42,360
Thank you.

448
00:32:50,150 --> 00:32:53,560
As you know, Military Prosecutor...

449
00:32:53,560 --> 00:32:59,570
As you know, this case is garnering lots of interest from the nation.

