00:33:14,830 --> 00:33:16,580
What you really think, not what you said to the press.

456
00:33:16,580 --> 00:33:18,920
How would I know?

457
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:22,740
I saved his brother. He's a bastard who bit the hand that fed him.

458
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:25,930
Could you write an appeal for clemency?

459
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,590
An appeal for clemency?

460
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:33,370
If you would write an appeal for clemency, it would be considered.

461
00:33:33,370 --> 00:33:35,560
Do you see the state of my leg? Yet you're asking for mercy?

462
00:33:35,560 --> 00:33:37,580
On top of it as a military prosecutor?

463
00:33:37,580 --> 00:33:42,180
Whether he shot a real bullet or a blank, he shot at his superior!

464
00:33:42,180 --> 00:33:45,280
This is treason of the highest form!

465
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:50,450
Even if he were severely punished as a warning to others, it would be not enough! Understand?

466
00:33:50,450 --> 00:33:54,890
Leaking of military secrets is a serious treasonous crime that sells out the country.

467
00:33:54,890 --> 00:34:00,050
Even if Chairman Cha Ho Cheol was severely punished as a warning to others, it would be not enough.

468
00:34:00,050 --> 00:34:02,580
No need to worry.

469
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:07,680
As you wish, I'll be sure

470
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:10,580
to make this incident a clear example.

471
00:34:10,580 --> 00:34:12,180
Good.

472
00:34:12,950 --> 00:34:15,030
I'll see you in court.

473
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:17,460
Sure. Work hard.

474
00:34:37,410 --> 00:34:39,170
Excuse me.

475
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:43,090
How is he doing?

476
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:46,640
It's not life threatening because life saving measures were rapidly done.

477
00:34:46,640 --> 00:34:50,240
The CT scan showed there is a piece of shrapnel in his brain

478
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:52,230
but we haven't removed it yet.

479
00:34:52,230 --> 00:34:55,210
We didn't want to risk complications that could arise from the removal.

480
00:34:59,670 --> 00:35:01,730
He's lucky he's alive.

481
00:35:07,290 --> 00:35:09,770
Is this really lucky?

482
00:35:14,300 --> 00:35:16,550
They had a great relationship, the brothers.

483
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:21,970
