486
00:35:28,900 --> 00:35:34,120
Even though they restrain his arms and legs, he keeps trying to escape.

487
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:36,130
I don't think he avoided brain damage.

488
00:35:36,130 --> 00:35:40,150
He couldn't recognize people, but kept saying he needed to go somewhere.

489
00:35:40,150 --> 00:35:43,700
It's not feasible for him to return to a normal lifestyle.

490
00:35:57,900 --> 00:36:02,130
I'm not defending Kim Han Yong's actions,

491
00:36:02,130 --> 00:36:06,300
but I think I'd also lose it if a family member became like this in a day.

492
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:14,420
Why didn't you report to me the division commander's visit to the law department?

493
00:36:14,420 --> 00:36:17,640
Because I knew you'd react this way.

494
00:36:17,640 --> 00:36:21,620
She just came for morale. There's no need for concern.

495
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:23,730
It's good for morale, right?

496
00:36:23,730 --> 00:36:26,250
You didn't do anything that would upset her, did you?

497
00:36:26,250 --> 00:36:28,460
No, well, not as far as I know.

498
